OL,3,CPlans for job cuts announced at one of
OL,4,CWales' main universities
OL,6,FSwansea University is looking to cut
OL,7,Fstaff across a range of disciplines,
OL,8,Fit has announced.
OL,10,FIt's thought 55 jobs could be lost out
OL,11,Fof a total of 204 roles, with the
OL,12,Finstitution saying it needs to 'make
OL,13,Fsavings to ensure its future financial
OL,14,Fsustainability.'
OL,16,FThe university says compulsory
OL,17,Fredundancy remains a 'measure of last
OL,18,Fresort; and to date it has made
OL,19,Fsavings through the management of
OL,20,Fvacancies and a 'generous voluntary
OL,21,Fexit' scheme for staff.
