OL,3,CPlans for job cuts announced at one of
OL,4,CWales' main universities
OL,6,FFaculty of Science and Engineering:
OL,8,FA Swansea University spokesperson
OL,9,Fsaid: "The UK Higher Education sector
OL,10,Fis facing a number of challenges,
OL,11,Fexacerbated by significant changes to
OL,12,Fthe international student recruitment
OL,13,Fcontext. In common with many other
OL,14,Funiversities, Swansea University needs
OL,15,Fto make savings to ensure our future
OL,16,Ffinancial sustainability.
