OL,3,CPlans for job cuts announced at one of
OL,4,CWales' main universities
OL,6,F"To date, we have made progress
OL,7,Ftowards securing those savings through
OL,8,Fthe careful management of vacancies
OL,9,Fand the provision of a generous
OL,10,FVoluntary Exit Scheme for staff.
OL,12,F"In some academic areas, we have
OL,13,Fdeveloped draft proposals to secure
OL,14,Fthe remainder of the savings we
OL,15,Frequire this year. We are now
OL,16,Fconsulting on these draft proposals
OL,17,Fwith our Campus Unions and colleagues.
