OL,6,F"As compulsory redundancy remains a
OL,7,Fmeasure of last resort, we are also
OL,8,Fproviding a further Voluntary Exit
OL,9,FScheme opportunity to academic
OL,10,Fcolleagues in those areas where
OL,11,Ffurther savings are still required.
OL,13,F"We continue to engage with our Campus
OL,14,FUnions to explore all opportunities
OL,15,Ffor redundancy mitigation across our
OL,16,Fcommunity.
