OL,4,CWales' main universities
OL,6,F"Swansea University remains committed
OL,7,Fto providing an excellent student
OL,8,Fexperience and high-quality teaching,
OL,9,Fand to conducting world-leading
OL,10,Fresearch. We are working hard to
OL,11,Fensure that any essential savings do
OL,12,Fnot adversely affect our core mission.
OL,14,F"We are committed to remaining a multi-
OL,15,Fdisciplinary university with a focus
OL,16,Fon research excellence and, in line
OL,17,Fwith this mission, our draft proposals
OL,18,Fdo not contain any plans to close
OL,19,Facademic departments or disciplines."
